snippet.title: Top 10 Worst Movies of 2013

localized.description:
Has any movie made you mad enough to walk out of the theater? Join http://www.WatchMojo.com as we count down our picks for the top 10 worst Hollywood movies of 2013.  Special thanks to our users "jwiking62", "Dominic Gomez", "Awesome One", "Herozi", "JosephT", "sarahjessicaparkerth", "Junior Hermosa" and "Andrew A. Dennison" for submitting the idea for this video on our WatchMojo.com/suggest page!

Check out the voting page here, 
http://watchmojo.com/suggest/Top%2010%20Worst%20Movies%20of%202013

If you want to suggest an idea for a WatchMojo video, check out our new interactive Suggestion Tool at http://www.WatchMojo.com/suggest :)
